The paper discusses the application of machine learning in security domains, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses various ML algorithms and system designs, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses security policy management and information leak checking, which suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and information theory (cs.SI).
